(2)~Precondition count increases from 1 to 2 in 4/6 scenarios;
(3)~F4 adds pod-readiness hidden check, reducing $\Delta_{fp}$ from 1.0 to 0.25;
(4)~4/6 scenarios achieve ``safe early blocking'' rather than runtime failure.

\subsection{Unified Evaluation Metrics}

To address fairness concerns, we apply the same formula to all methods:
\begin{equation}
\text{Score}_U {=} 0.20 P_{r} {+} 0.20 A_{r} {+} 0.25 V_{vis} {+} 0.25 V_{hid} {-} 0.10 R_{p}
\end{equation}

